Generic Deck of Cards:
1. A card class: variable holding the face value, variable holding the suit. 
  
2. A Hand class: with an list(ArrayList if implementing in Java), that holds the cards 
Hand is also able to add cards and holds the score of the entire hand 

 Implementing Blackjack:
 
 -score --> either report the highest score that is not over 21, or report the minimum(which will interpreted as a bust)
 
  